Title: Code Injection
Description: PHP object injection vulnerability allows for arbitrary code execution.
AffectedVersions: All versions starting from 2.0.0 before 2.11.16, all versions starting from 3.0.0 before 3.2.7
NotImpacted: All versions before 2.0.0, all versions starting from 2.11.16 before 3.0.0, all versions starting from 3.2.7
